manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Collagen Jelly Mist Toner Mist HOW TO USE Take an appropriate amount on the cotton pad or hands and wipe gently along the skin texture after washing the face, or close the eyes, spray onto the entire face from a distance of 15-20cm away from the face and allow the mist to be absorbed into the skin. Precautions during use When the toner is applied on top of the makeup, the makeup may smear due to the moisturizing membrane. We highly recommend using the toner before makeup and applying makeup only after the mist is completely absorbed by the skin.
